<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><h2>What is MyLab Nutrition</h2>

<p>MyLab Nutrition was born in 2018 from the dream of <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/gianlucaperra">Gianluca Perra</a>
to bring into the supplements market an innovative solution to create completely personalised formulas.</p>

<p>Gianluca, coming from the experience he has since 2016 with his brand <strong>T-Rex Integratori</strong>, together with
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/danielefumi/">Daniele Fumi</a> proposed the project
to <a href="https://lventuregroup.com?utm_source=italianprogrammer.pizza">LVenture Group</a>
